{"tid":2379270,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高文堅持放阿蘇非錯誤","createTime":"2021-01-25T06:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T06:22:37.000Z","uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bb4556b820624a6c1fbb979210abd912a17b09e7","tid":2379270,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:19:17.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】巴塞隆拿教練朗奴高文堅持，放走射手蘇亞雷斯不是錯誤的決定。<br />\n巴塞隆拿今季深受進攻疲弱困擾，難免令人懷念被逼離隊的蘇亞雷斯，後者加盟馬德里體育會後入球率仍然高企。朗奴高文（Ronald Koeman）說：「我不喜歡回答這樣的問題，他是好球員，但我們作出了決定。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然企硬放走阿蘇是正確決定，但高文承認一眾前鋒表現欠佳，上場便射失了2記12碼，「如果看看我們的12碼，今季有12個，射失了7個，太多了。要是美斯不在陣中，我們需要另一位劊子手。」 <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"><a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/sports/高文堅持放阿蘇非錯誤-021304600.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fsports%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%96%87%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81%E6%94%BE%E9%98%BF%E8%98%87%E9%9D%9E%E9%8C%AF%E8%AA%A4-021304600.html&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=ea365be0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/sports/高文堅持放阿蘇非錯誤-021304600.html</a></span>"},{"pid":"4723110eae697ef2cf018316e2b3368ff4a4fff4","tid":2379270,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:19:29.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"2f180b8acd17f870050d775e96c50168e3726033","tid":2379270,"uid":313905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:22:37.000Z","msg":"bill 哥重返波台帶手兄贏錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}